<CSSLayerBlockRule>
<summary>
The <strong><c>CSSLayerBlockRule</c></strong> represents a <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@layer">@layer</see> block rule. It is a grouping at-rule meaning that it can contain other rules, and is associated to a given cascade layer, identified by its <strong>name</strong>.
</summary>
<remarks>
